  "title": "LIVE STREAMER & SOCIAL MEDIA MARKETING EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p>We are an established and renowned educational publisher in Singapore since 1977. We are looking for a passionate and energetic presenter for live streaming of our products, assessment books.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>This position is open for full-time, project based or contract engagement.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>• To summarize and deliver product information in text and video format.</p>\n<p>• Plan and execute engaging live streams that promote our brand and engage our audience, and achieve sales targets.</p>\n<p>• Collaborate with other team members to create compelling content for live streams</p>\n<p>• Monitor and respond to comments and questions from viewers during live streams</p>\n<p>• Able to comfortably deliver video scripts on camera for live social media streams and pre-recorded videos</p>\n<p>• Represent the brand in a professional manner during live streams</p>\n<p>• Edit new videos</p>\n<p>• Maintain and manage streaming equipment and software</p>\n<p>• Stay up-to-date with emerging trends and technologies in live-streaming</p>\n<p>• Analyse data and feedback to continuously improve the quality of our live streams</p>\n<p>• Participate in team meetings and contribute to the development of our live-streaming strategy</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>• Proven experience as a live streamer</p>\n<p>• Has excellent on-camera presentation skills</p>\n<p>• Strong knowledge of social media platforms and live-streaming applications</p>\n<p>• Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>• Strong organizational and time-management skills</p>\n<p>• Ability to work independently and as part of a team</p>\n<p>• Flexibility to work outside of regular business hours as required</p>\n<p>• A portfolio of previous live streams or video content is highly desirable.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>The ideal candidate:</strong></p>\n<p>• Passion about writing and creating interesting stories</p>\n<p>• Good time-management skills</p>\n<p>• Computer proficiency (MS Office, digital editing, web search, databases)</p>\n<p>• Familiar with social media and live streaming platforms</p>\n<p>• Able to work independently with minimum supervision</p>\n<p>• High attention to details</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please send in your resume to <a href=\"mailto:sharonyoo@sapgrp.com\">sharonyoo@sapgrp.com</a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Remuneration will be commensurate with qualifications and experience. Fresh graduates are welcome to apply.</p>\n<p><br>\nPlease submit your resume together with a cover letter, and include any relevant portfolio, blog, recordings, or videos, if available.<br>\n</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
